Panthers Pro Bowl Linebacker Jon Beason to Miss Entire Season With Injury

-- B y   J a y   B e b e r m a n
-- 
2011-09-13T13:06:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-13/panthers-pro-bowl-linebacker-jon-beason-to-miss-entire-season-with-injury.html
Carolina Panthers  Pro Bowl 
linebacker Jon Beason will miss the season after tearing his
left Achilles tendon in a loss to the  Arizona Cardinals  on Sept.
11, the National Football League team said on its website.  Beason, 26, led the team in tackles every year since
joining the league in 2007 and has made the Pro Bowl three
times.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jay Beberman at 
 jbeberman@bloomberg.net  